    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Usually diagnosed by clinical suspicion\nLumbar puncture\nif any concern for\nHSV\n,\nVZV\n, or\nbacterial meningitis\nCan test CSF for Japanese encephalitis",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": [
