    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Supportive\nIVF\n,\nelectrolyte repletion\n, antipyretics\nAntiepileptics\nfor seizures\nDepressed mental status may require intubation for airway protection\nConsider empiric\nacyclovir\nand\nantibiotics\nif HSV or bacterial causes not ruled out",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
